The PhEur 6.5 and {{ drug.molecular_formula }}–NF27 describe anhydrous lactose as Ob-

D-galactopyranosyl-(1!4)-b-D-glucopyranose; or a mixture of

O-b-D-galactopyranosyl-(1!4)-a-D-glucopyranose and O-b-Dgalactopyranosyl-(

